name: 甜花
text:
ごめんなさい……
甜花、ダメだった……

name: プロデューサー
trans: Tenka, you don't have to apolo──...

name: 甜花
text:
甜花、ダメだったのに……
……頑張れたの……ここまで、これたの……嬉しいって……
trans:
Even though... Tenka wasn't good enough...... she was
able to work hard... she made it this far... and she was
so happy......

name: 甜花
text:
ダメ、だったのに……
ごめんなさい……
trans: Even if... she wasn't good enough...... sorry......

name: プロデューサー
trans: ......It's okay. I'm proud of you, Tenka.
